l-time assessment of correlation, generalization, robustness, and coherence under one coherent architecture. Crucially, DAEG also supports counterfactual probing—e.g., “How would this metric score change if the topic transition were less smooth?”—enabling interpretability and diagnostic capabilities absent in prior work.

