iors via lightweight fine-tuning or adapter modules. This creates a self-evolving evaluation ecosystem capable of detecting emergent failure modes (e.g., hallucination masking as coherence) and adapting to novel domains with minimal supervision. By formalizing evaluation as a cognitive act rather than a mechanical computation, CogEval-Graph offers a paradigm shift toward transparent, context-sensitive, and psychologically plausible metric assessment. Its release will include a new benchmark, CogBench, featuring human-labeled reasoning trajectories across summarization, dialogue, and creative writing tasks.",
